snippet.title: Rust Console Edition - Out May 21st Pre-Order Now! | ESRB
snippet.description:
Pre-orders are now live for Rust Console Edition. Check the marketplace and be sure to get your copy of the game! Visit our website for more information: https://rust.double11.com/ 

Be sure to follow our Social Media page to keep up with the latest Rust Console News.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/playrustconsole
